## Introduction

Import teeth data

```{r import}
teeth <- read.csv("data/teeth.csv", row.names = 1)
head(teeth)
```

#Boxplot

Create boxplots related to the data

```{r boxplot}
boxplot(len ~ dose, data = teeth)
boxplot(len ~ supp, data = teeth)
boxplot(len ~ dose + supp, data = teeth)
```

#Permutation

```{r pm}
summary(teeth)
```
